y":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"推到黨鐵仆街為止"},{"pid":"f8e15f0921ba9b067f5c48b8e00f001414329351","tid":1554404,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26187c1106ed6bae9ee7ed93cf73d359304926a0","tid":1554404,"uid":119467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"044f002483a5314c277c2e54fcb762d6b7b68e59","tid":1554404,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e9d97bcfc9593f3d5e29d835e6894e70ea52131","tid":1554404,"uid":245473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"唔知大家知唔知係瑞典，全線斯德哥爾摩地鐵而家都係以合約專營權方式，交由<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黨鐵旗下嘅公司 MTR Nordic AB 營運</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n為呼應攬炒巴打團隊登報行動，我朋友都略盡綿力去延續呢條國際戰線，Send左封信去一個瑞典專講人權嘅社交平台出post，講述香港示威者嘅遭遇同黨鐵有幾仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。Follow得呢個IG嘅人都係關心人權嘅瑞典人，相信都會有一定效果，已經見到有留言話應該要終止黨鐵係瑞典嘅合約！<br />\n<br />\n我地希望可以係當地<span style=\"color: red;\">製造輿論</span>，最終目標係：<br />\n1 推廣黨鐵係香港處理示威嘅手法有幾唔人道，政府/鐵路擁有者<span style=\"color: red;\">停止讓黨鐵繼續取得專營權營運當地地鐵</span>！<br />\n2 廣告商減少落廣告比當地地鐵，<span style=\"color: red;\">斷黨鐵背後廣告收益財路</span>！<br />\n<br />\n暫時呢個IG 平台雖然只有約七萬幾人睇，但星星之火可以燎原。大家有時間可以入去like/share post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最緊要係<span style=\"color: red;\">留言呼籲讀者要send email去有份投資MTR Nordic AB或者落廣告嘅金主度申訴</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/tnkvrt?igshid=g6xjeba9ijva\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftnkvrt%3Figshid%3Dg6xjeba9ijva&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=c0e151ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/tnkvrt?igshid=g6xjeba9ijva</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZAH6Ty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZAH6Ty.jpg&h=4c385baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dS68h0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdS68h0d.jpg&h=a592fcff&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:16:23.000Z","msg":"一齊推"},{"pid":"b85d42ac82d540bedf3c46d93e537fe839e8b627","tid":1554404,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"55b7ea7084262137df2625661f64e105c83cc4d7","tid":1554404,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f854d248a4f28e01e6eda296530d5f5396e7613","tid":1554404,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"仲有英國同澳洲都有業務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298b22a0e26124e7bb72077ff4005e58c89bb617","tid":1554404,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"趁瑞典同共狗鬧返咗<br />\n<br />\nCONNECT北歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得挪威同丹麥已經有出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29505a32536c5b4287f265ef512f62f6029aaa23","tid":1554404,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096a10de17df86cfbb6d967f4f477521fd8dfa21","tid":1554404,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"其實反而瑞典要迫mtr要轉移管理模式好過<br />\n深圳同其他內地城市鐵路系統發展快既主要原因就係中共偷咗英治留落嚟既地鐵同九鐵 偷咗硬件加軟件 冇研究代價 抄就得<br />\n但支那人會話自己富強發展快 其實係靠偷香港嘢<br />\n只要香港冇既嘢 支那都係收皮 細至原子筆走珠 晶片 到飛機引擎"},{"pid":"aaa33ca483a0b880